OL,3,CMan denies dumping dead hares and
OL,4,Cprotected birds outside village shop
OL,6,FA father-of-three has denied dumping
OL,7,Fthe bodies of 50 hares outside a
OL,8,Fvillage shop in what has been
OL,9,Fdescribed as a "horror movie scene".
OL,11,FJames Kempster, 39, who lives at a
OL,12,Fcaravan site in Totton in Southampton,
OL,13,Fis on trial at Southampton
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court charged with two
OL,15,Fcounts of possessing a dead bird under
OL,16,Fthe Wildlife and Countryside Act and a
OL,17,Fcharge of criminal damage to the shop
OL,18,Ffront.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@cO]
