OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777047070
OL,3,CMan denies dumping dead hares and
OL,4,Cprotected birds outside village shop
OL,6,FThe court heard the incident was
OL,7,Fcaught on CCTV outside Broughton
OL,8,FCommunity Shop in the early hours of
OL,9,FMarch 15, 2024.
OL,11,FAdam Cooper, prosecuting, has told the
OL,12,Fcourt the footage shows three men
OL,13,Farrive in a car with two men wearing
OL,14,Fbalaclavas getting out and dumping the
OL,15,Fhares.
OL,17,FThe car was found burnt out in a
OL,18,Fcountry lane after the incident, the
OL,19,Fcourt has heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
