PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777047070
OL,3,CMan denies dumping dead hares and
OL,4,Cprotected birds outside village shop
OL,6,FThe prosecution claim that DNA from
OL,7,Ftwo people found on one of the dead
OL,8,Fbirds was a billion times more likely
OL,9,Fto have come from Kempster and an
OL,10,Funknown individual than from two
OL,11,Findividuals not related to the
OL,12,Fdefendant.
OL,14,FGiving evidence, Kempster denied being
OL,15,Fthe man shown on the CCTV putting the
OL,16,Fhares in front of the shop and the two
OL,17,Fbirds under the door handles.
OL,19,FWhen asked what he was doing that
OL,20,Fnight, he said: "I can't remember last
OL,21,Fweek let alone two years ago."
OL,26,@|D@QOU}D@^O]
