PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777047070
OL,3,CMan denies dumping dead hares and
OL,4,Cprotected birds outside village shop
OL,6,FMr Cooper asked the defendant how his
OL,7,FDNA was found at the scene. Kempster
OL,8,Freplied: "The only way I can explain
OL,9,Fit is transferable DNA."
OL,11,FThe defendant also denied burning out
OL,12,Fthe car used in the incident.
OL,14,FKempster denies the charges and the
OL,15,Ftrial continues.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@XO]
